<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Schweinfurt, Windsheim und Weißenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet, in acht Tagen Gesandte zu einer Besprechung nach Nürnberg zu schicken.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="5r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_11_r2l19">Sweinfürt / <expan>Winſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> . vnd <expan>VVeiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_11_r2l21"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / einen brief geſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l22">vnd auch ein abſchrift domit / als vvir ew 
<del rend="strikethrough">das </del> der abſchrifte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l23">ſenden <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloʒʒen</expan> in diſem briefe / . vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr erſamkeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l24">daʒ Jr ewr erber botſchaft darvmb cʒü vns <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l25">Alſo / daʒ die auf den freÿtag als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> hewte v̈ber Acht tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l26">cʒü Ratcʒeit beÿ vns ſeÿ / . vnd das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvinſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l27">vnd <expan>weiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auch alſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l28"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l1">daʒ vvir ew </ab><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l2">des <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l3"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab></add> daʒ ſie die Jren auch alſo her cʒü vns ſchıcken / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l29"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>vj̃</expan> . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidij / ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="5r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Sweinfürt, <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die von
                                                  <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> einen brief
                                                gesant und auch ein abschrift domit, als wir ew der
                                                abschrifte senden <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slozzen</expan>
                                                in disem briefe. Und <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                ewr ersamkeit, daz ir ewr erber botschaft darumb czü
                                                uns <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, also
                                          daz die auf den <app><note><q type="date">freytag</q>06.09.1409</note></app> als
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> hewte über acht tag
                                                czü ratczeit bey uns sey. Und das
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auch also
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, <add>daz wir ew
                                                  des <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und</add> daz sie
                                                die iren auch also her czü uns schicken.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>vi</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
